## [2026-06-29 23:15 UTC] MODULE_02_RECON / MODULE_17_SOCIAL_ENGINEERING — DNS Recon
**Target:** Public infrastructure (github.com)
**Command:** `nslookup -type=TXT _dmarc.github.com`
**Result:** DMARC record returned: `v=DMARC1; p=quarantine; sp=reject; pct=100; rua=mailto:dmarc@github.com; ruf=mailto:dmarc@github.com; fo=1`
**Finding:** GitHub has strict DMARC policy (quarantine/reject). Email spoofing GitHub directly would fail or be quarantined.
**Module impact:** Added to MODULE_17_SOCIAL_ENGINEERING as live evidence box.

