## [2026-06-30 00:45 UTC] MODULE_16_C2 — Domain Fronting Deprecated
**Target:** MODULE_16_C2.html content
**Research:** AWS CloudFront and Google App Engine patched domain fronting in 2018-2021. Microsoft Azure followed. Major CDNs now validate Host header against TLS SNI.
**Finding:** Domain fronting is no longer reliable for C2. Still possible on misconfigured CDNs but not a general technique.
**Module impact:** Added deprecation warning box to MODULE_16_C2.

